data.description: ***** PRICE JUST IMPROVED ***** Introducing a stunning 4-bed, 3.5-bath gem in San Antonio, TX! Nestled in River Ranch, this home offers serene living with modern luxury. Open-concept living, high ceilings, and abundant natural light create an inviting atmosphere. The chef's kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless appliances, and a spacious island. The primary suite features a spa-like bath with a soaking tub and walk-in shower. Enjoy outdoor living on the covered patio with fireplace, and explore the vast backyard. This property is a rare find - a perfect blend of comfort and elegance. Don't miss out!
